        <div class="details">
            <p>{{_ Legality is determined at the release of a Standard-legal set on Magic Online.}}</p>
            <p>{{_ Prices are checked every hour for a week. Anything 1c or less for half or more of all checks is legal for the season.}}</p>
            <p>{{_ Cards from the just-released set are added (nothing removed) a couple of weeks later via a supplemental rotation after prices have settled a little.}}</p>
